:IMAGE:
:LAYOUT:vertical
:ANSWERORDER:randomized
:INDICES:letters
:ANSWER1:100:H
A larger current will flow through the short, thick wire.
:ANSWER2:0:H
A larger current will flow through the long, thin wire.
:ANSWER3:0:H
The currents through the two wires will be the same.
